%N A156222 Triangle T(n, k, q) = q^k*Q(k, n, q), with T(0, 0, q) = -2, where Q(k, n, q) = (1/q)*( -Q(k-1, n, q) + (1+q)*p(q, k-1)^n), Q(k, 0, q) = -q*(1+q)^n, p(q, n) = Product_{j=1..n} ( (1-q^k)/(1-q) ), and q = 2, read by rows.
